name: INTELTEQ
tag_list: sematics, semantic-topology, intelteq, intelpuzzle, vselector, big-data, linked-data, mdm, education, game
overview:
Center of Intelligent Information Technologies INTELTEQ, a small but fast-growing Russian company that specializes in semantic modeling. The company was included in Gartner’s list of Cool Vendors in Information Governance and MDM (Master Data Management) 2013 report. The company utilizes a semantic modeling tool called Semantic Topology.

INTELTEQ is not a software company. It provides methodology and consulting services for top management while helping to recognize and assign semantic value to Master Data at all stages of information governance.

As a new direction of development there is set of products ready to be launched upon fundrasing: INTELTEQ’s IntelPuzzle (www.intelpuzzle.com - Freemium Educational Game for iPad) or INTETEQ’s VSelector (www.vselector.com - Semantic Streaming Video Management)
